{"tid":2092109,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩院通過《港自治法案》 美擬懲京官業務往來銀行","createTime":"2020-07-03T04:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T05:28:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e956d2cd0df4d75794997c1a6c63c64f3bf09ff8","tid":2092109,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/OT4Y6J3OFODF5JMDSBGSXMVTHU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FOT4Y6J3OFODF5JMDSBGSXMVTHU%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=0e5786d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FOT4Y6J3OFODF5JMDSBGSXMVTHU%2F&h=62b5216e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/OT4Y6J3OFODF5JMDSBGSXMVTHU/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩院通過《港自治法案》<br />\n美擬懲京官業務往來銀行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】針對港版國安法正式落實，美國國會眾議院前日一致通過《香港自治法案》，向違反《中英聯合聲明》及《基本法》下中國對香港承諾的中方個人和實體，包括香港警方實施嚴厲制裁，法案亦涉及與中國推行港版國安法官員有業務來往的銀行。法案跟早前參議院通過的有些微不同，昨日再經參院通過，等待總統特朗普簽署落實。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒隨時中招 譚耀宗：明眼人識分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WLykjHumxrg_mV5w1s1PivMPVNI=/639x529/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JWN7XDSSPBA22KZXK7IIYKBYXU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWLykjHumxrg_mV5w1s1PivMPVNI%3D%2F639x529%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJWN7XDSSPBA22KZXK7IIYKBYXU.jpg&h=2cb9af47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共和黨參議員圖米發言時，擺放了香港抗爭者示威的圖片。Hong Kong Watch圖片<br />\n<br />\n眾議院議長佩洛西在眾院表決前發言，說「中國政府以為可以打壓民主精神而不用面對懲罰。若我們為了商業利益拒絕為中國的人權發聲，就會失去在世界任何地方為人權發聲的道德權威」。她較早時罕有現身有關香港情況的眾院外交事務委員會聽證會，並發言指港版國安法宣佈「一國兩制」死亡，「殘酷、全面鎮壓香港人，意圖摧毀他們獲承諾的自由」。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院最終全票通過法<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n以成為國際金融中心的自治地位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vZ0flIw9KkJfS6D02hzfBfg_qAw=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UN2V3N4HYU5OGDVS2ZQYSBC6J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvZ0flIw9KkJfS6D02hzfBfg_qAw%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUN2V3N4HYU5OGDVS2ZQYSBC6J4.jpg&h=9e2bcf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國參眾兩院通過《香港自治法案》，統一版本再交總統簽署。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將交總統簽署<br />\n<br />\n參議院上周已通過類似法案，但<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n普一直未有表態會否簽署。<br />\n<br />\n副總統彭斯昨日受訪<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n全世界愛好自由的人所接受」。<br />\n<br />\n對於美國眾院通過《香港自治法案》，中國外交部發言人趙<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n的『美麗風景線』。」他建議對方「還是把『美麗的風景線』留給自己吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vUuu_Kbc5vbVJcN_T9nRM5e7anc=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AC6Q4VYUL4G2K7GSW7TO5XIH7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvUuu_Kbc5vbVJcN_T9nRM5e7anc%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAC6Q4VYUL4G2K7GSW7TO5XIH7M.jpg&h=345e5998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾議院議長佩洛西日前指港版國安法宣佈「一國兩制」死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拜登揚言更強硬<br />\n<br />\n另外，篤定成為民主黨總統候選人的拜登，就批評特朗普<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n國公民、公司或機構滅聲，「我將會迅即實施經濟制裁」。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"546ff0e6ea885034604422e75693c8fbf84deae1","tid":2092109,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"唔俾我講光復香港？咁我咪播囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2092108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2092108</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f58436ea4ae36e06b29a22746dd2e6dd354389c2","tid":2092109,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/